<p>I thought some of the Ext JS objects would translate directly into non-div html tags. Why is everything a <code>&lt;div&gt;</code> in element view when viewing my app in debug mode?  I never see any <code>&lt;button&gt;</code>,<code>&lt;img&gt;</code>,<code>&lt;a&gt;</code> or any other usual html tag.  </p>  <p>For clarification: <a href="http://i.stack.imgur.com/sX80D.png" rel="nofollow"><img src="http://i.stack.imgur.com/sX80D.png" alt="screenshot"></a></p>